---
title: Camembert, Balsamic Onion and Mushroom Wellingtons with Roast Potatoes, Tenderstem Broccoli and Redcurrant Sauce
description: These Camembert, Balsamic Onion and Mushroom Wellingtons are bursting full of flavours and make the perfect dinner night option, from HelloFresh. Cook up a fresh start!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/camembert-balsamic-onion-and-mushroom-wellingtons-91827253-6944044a.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/camembert-balsamic-onion-and-mushroom-wellingtons-5fbfd40b5e1f147e476e3615-b10231c4.pdf
